{"data":[{"date":"12:16 24/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u1edbm Anh vs Panama","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/link-xem-anh-vs-panama.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T Anh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u1eeda c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Panama. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Panama tin r\u1eb1ng 90 ph\u00fat c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-anh-vs-panama-463-189421.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/link-xem-anh-vs-panama.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-anh-vs-panama-463-189421.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Anh vs Panama 19h00 ng\u00e0y 24/6 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Anh vs Panama: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs Panama b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>\u0110T Anh th\u1eafng 3-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1:</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: </em>Anh vs Panama<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian:</em> 19h ng\u00e0y 24/6<br>\r\n<em> \u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>S\u00e2n Nizhny Novgorod<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em> TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>Anh -0.91*0:1 3/4*0.86 Panama<br>\r\n<em> TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn:</em> Nhi\u1ec1u 0.86*2 1/2*-0.93 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Panama v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o tr\u00ean Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Panama v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, soi k\u00e8o tr\u00ean Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-panama-va-du-doan-soi-keo-panama-vs-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Panama 19h ng\u00e0y 24/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1i c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 B\u1ec9 v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Tunisia 5-2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi \u0110T Anh. \u0110\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c v\u00f4 h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Tam s\u01b0 l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00eam n\u1eefa, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Anh \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018. \u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Tunisia 2-1 \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u00e0 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 khi l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 cho m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi 5-2 Tunisia\" title=\"B\u1ec9 5-2 Tunisia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/231459-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u1ec9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tunisia 5-2</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb World Cup 2006, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Paraguay 1-0 t\u1edbi nay, \u0110T Anh m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng khi ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. 2 k\u1ef3 c\u00fap th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1eeba qua, Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 v\u00e0 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n s\u1edbm. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, v\u1edbi b\u1ec7 ph\u00f3ng l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m khi m\u1edbi b\u01b0\u1edbc ra s\u00e2n c\u1ecf n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga, h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c l\u1ea1c quan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Panama c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i suy \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Panama qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi Anh v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd c\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n then ch\u1ed1t l\u00e0 b\u1edfi tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb khu v\u1ef1c CONCACAF \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tunisia 1-2 Anh Harry Kane\" title=\"Tunisia 1-2 Anh Harry Kane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/diem-nhan-tran-tunisia-12-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110T&nbsp;Anh kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u1edf World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng, Panama v\u1eabn th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u00f4i l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Trung M\u1ef9 l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu trong c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Panama \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 r\u00f5 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Qua \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Panama b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0110T Anh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 v\u00e9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Hernan Gomez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bi 3-0 Panama\" title=\"B\u1ec9 3-0 Panama\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Bi-3-0-Panama-Khi-moi-loi-khen-di-kem-voi-mot-chu-nhung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Panama th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-3 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean b\u1ecb xem l\u00e0 &ldquo;l\u00f3t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng&rdquo; nh\u01b0 Panama l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Anh ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh. V\u1edbi ri\u00eang ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane, anh c\u00f2n m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ri\u00eang l\u00e0 chinh ph\u1ee5c danh hi\u1ec7u Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi. Kane v\u00e0 Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn khi r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia v\u00e0 Panama.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc Tunisia, Kane \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd. Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Romelu Lukaku ghi 4 b\u00e0n sau 2 tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi Tunisia v\u00e0 Panama, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ch\u00e2n s\u00fat thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Tottenham \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01a1n th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Kane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf CLB v\u00e0 gi\u1edd ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh r\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y. HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 trao chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Kane v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng anh s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00e0u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Harry Kane\" title=\"tien dao Harry Kane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/hlv-southgate-phat-bieu-ve-kane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kane l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Anh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Panama tin r\u1eb1ng Kane s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i. C\u1ea3 v\u00ec m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea3 v\u00ec \u0110TQG, anh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ghi th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n. C\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t r\u1ed9ng, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 Euro 2016 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean n\u1ed7i \u0111au.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110T Anh c\u1ea7n s\u1edbm ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t &ldquo;\u0111\u00eam d\u00e0i l\u1eafm m\u1ed9ng&rdquo; b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama. M\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra: Sau khi s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Anh \u0111\u1ea9y Panama v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u00e2ng cao \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Khi \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra v\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ea5y tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi Tunisia h\u00f4m qua l\u00e0m v\u00ed d\u1ee5. Sau khi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf, nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 thi nhau b\u1eafn ph\u00e1 khung th\u00e0nh Tunisia. Nh\u1eefng m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd nh\u01b0 Eden Hazard hay Lukaku \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u1edbi m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn Michy Batshuayi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong hi\u1ec7p 2 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 1. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi g\u1ee3i l\u00ean nh\u1eefng suy ngh\u0129 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>Nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>\u0110T Anh th\u1eafng 3-0</strong></div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 10 (O 9 1/2)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 5 (O 4 1/2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Panama trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn s\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n (-1)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Panama trong hi\u1ec7p 1 s\u1ebd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n (-1/4)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Panama trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng thua qu\u00e1 5 (+5)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"534","checkdouble":"189416"},{"date":"13:08 24/06","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-duc-21-thuy-dien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Toni Kroos</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Toni Kroos \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m v\u1edbi Sebastian Rudy, sau khi ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Bayern d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 r\u1eddi s\u00e2n s\u1edbm th\u00ec Kroos \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Gundogan. D\u00f9 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o th\u00ec ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real v\u1eabn ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-Duc-vs-Thuy-Dien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Toni Kroos ghi b\u00e0n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ec7 Toni Kroos th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t con qu\u00e1i v\u1eadt \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, anh v\u1eeba l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 thu h\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng, ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i, \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKroos ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 144 l\u1ea7n (nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n), th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 121 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 93.6%. Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 17 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111i \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f2n n\u1eefa, Kroos c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng, 3 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 6 qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t. Ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Kroos th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp m\u1eabu m\u1ef1c gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nToni Kroos \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Mesut Ozil hay Thomas Muller m\u00e0 ch\u00ednh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Die Mannschaft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Jerome Boateng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Jerome Boateng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, trong hi\u1ec7p 1 anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f2n t\u1ecf ra thua thi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111ua t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tinh huong Boateng pham loi voi Forsberg trong vong cam DT Duc\" title=\"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Boateng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Forsberg trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/130053-boateng.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Boateng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Bayern Munich th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Emil Forsberg trong hi\u1ec7p 1, d\u00f9 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh song tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng 11m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111ang l\u00e0 1-1 v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u00ec Jerome Boateng l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 2 qua \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ea5t may cho Boateng l\u00e0 Toni Kroos \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0110\u1ee9c, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Marco Reus</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1, HLV Joachim Low \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Marco Reus \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111\u00e1 ngay sau trung phong Timo Werner. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Reus \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup, v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u0111\u1eadm n\u00e9t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Reus va man tro lai tuyet voi\" title=\"Reus v\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-o-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Reus g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMarco Reus thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, anh t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh. Reus th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Reus. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng sau c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n, sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Dortmund ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap Toni Kroos ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-o-world-cup-421-189402.html\" target=\"_blank\">Reus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</span>. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Janne Andersson \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi m\u00e0 c\u00f2n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1-0 sau 45 ph\u00fat.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Toivonen mo ty so cho Thuy Dien\" title=\"Toivonen m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/Ola-Toivonen-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Duc-vs-Thuy-Dien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2, Marco Reus gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1. Tuy nhi\u00ean Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1eabn b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh tri\u1ec3n khai l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00ec \u1edf ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Toni Kroos \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n mang v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 cho \u0110\u1ee9c. C\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Janne Andersson trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed5 s\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-duc-vs-thuy-dien-421-189372.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n </span>khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico m\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u M\u1ef9, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1eafng tay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Han Quoc vs Mexico\" title=\"H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/223052-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng mu\u1ed9n c\u1ee7a Son Heung-Min kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico. Tr\u1eadn thua 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u M\u1ef9 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 kim chi \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra. \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c duy tr\u00ec hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n thua Mexico, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Mesut Ozil</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Mexico \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, song m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a anh kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Low noi ve Mesut Ozil\" title=\"HLV Low n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/hlv-joachim-low-noi-gi-ve-quyet-dinh-loai-bo-mesut-ozil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Mesut Ozil kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ozil ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 1 l\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi\u1ebfn Ozil b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, anh ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Marco Reus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed khi r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng HLV Joachim Low c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hlv-joachim-low-noi-gi-ve-quyet-dinh-loai-bo-mesut-ozil-421-189410.html\" target=\"_blank\">Joachim Low ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ozil</span>, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988, song v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Reus, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng&nbsp;Ozil ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"533","checkdouble":"189417"},{"date":"16:31 24/06","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Panama e ng\u1ea1i Harry Kane","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/nguoi-cu-panama-e-ngai-harry-kane.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u HLV Julio Dely Valdes c\u1ee7a Panama cho r\u1eb1ng Harry Kane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Kane \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Tunisia. Pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd c\u1ee7a Kane \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f9ng kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho Tam S\u01b0 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKane \u0111ang d\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi hi\u1ec7n nay. Anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 20 b\u00e0n trong 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Panama e ng\u1ea1i Kane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Panama e ng\u1ea1i Kane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/nguoi-cu-panama-e-ngai-harry-kane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>C\u1ef1u HLV\u00a0Panama e ng\u1ea1i Kane</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u1edbi Panama, Kane s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 l\u0129nh x\u01b0\u1edbng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng tuy\u1ec3n Anh. V\u00e0 c\u1ef1u HLV Dely Valdes t\u1ecf ra lo ng\u1ea1i cho Panama v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a Kane.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTrong v\u00e0i n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Kane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Anh \u1ea5y ghi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cVai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, Kane c\u0169ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n Anh. V\u00e0 Panama ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Kane \u0111\u00e1 r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1edf h\u1eefu n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t l\u1eabn k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>2 ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Panama</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Panama \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 v\u00e0 Honduras \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1edbi Nga t\u1eeb khu v\u1ef1c CONCACAF. V\u00e0 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Panama v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh gi\u00e0 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Nga. V\u00e0 Dely Valdes \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean then ch\u1ed1t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u M\u0129.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cNh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia Panama hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1ecf h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jaime Penedo. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110TQG.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cRoman Torres c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 huy c\u1ee7a Panama \u1edf World Cup n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p h\u1ecd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n th\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Anh vs Panama:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-panama-va-du-doan-soi-keo-panama-vs-anh-421-189416.html\">Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u1edbm Anh vs Panama</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-anh-vs-panama-19h00-ngay-2406-ve-di-tiep-cho-tam-su-421-189401.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Anh vs Panama (19h00 ng\u00e0y 24/06): V\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp cho Tam s\u01b0?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"532","checkdouble":"189420"},{"date":"16:40 24/06","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Anh vs Panama 19h00 ng\u00e0y 24/6 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/link-xem-anh-vs-panama.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Anh vs Panama: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs Panama b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 24/6.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Anh vs Panama: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs Panama b\u1ea3ng G World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 24/6.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-anh-vs-panama-463-189421.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP ANH VS PANAMA</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"531","checkdouble":"189421"},{"date":"17:11 24/06","title":"N\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111ang \"r\u1ed1i nh\u01b0 canh h\u1eb9\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/24/noi-bo-tuyen-argentina-dang-roi-nhu-canh-he.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111ang r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng r\u1ed1i ren khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng khai th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea5t h\u00f2a v\u1edbi HLV Jorge Sampaoli trong khi c\u00e1c quan ch\u1ee9c c\u1ea5p cao l\u1ea1i ch\u01b0a d\u00e1m \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ea1nh tay.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Lionel Messi c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi x\u01b0\u1edbng phi v\u1ee5 \"\u0111\u1ea3o ch\u00ednh\" thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng 58 tu\u1ed5i b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 k\u00e9m c\u1ecfi v\u00e0 b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng 0-3 c\u1ee7a Albiceleste tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn, song Argentina v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u1edd v\u1ecb c\u1ee9u tinh mang t\u00ean Nigeria khi \"\u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh\" \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111ang r\u1ed1i nh\u01b0 canh h\u1eb9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111ang r\u1ed1i nh\u01b0 canh h\u1eb9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/NINTCHDBPICT0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mascherano \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ea7u vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea3o ch\u00ednh Sampaoli. \u1ea2nh: AFP.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Sampaoli c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh Nigeria \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi tr\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee3i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i Iceland vs Croatia \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00ea gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y v\u1eeba qua, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Argentina \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1edbi Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Argentina v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd m\u1ea5t h\u1ebft ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m d\u00e0nh cho \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Sampaoli.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp kh\u1ea9n c\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 6 v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a 23 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n, HLV Sampaoli, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Argentina Claudio Tapia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJavier Mascherano \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ea7u phi v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ea3o ch\u00ednh, y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nigeria di\u1ec5n ra. H\u1ecd mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorge Barruchaga, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 1986, hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG s\u1ebd l\u00ean thay th\u1ebf HLV Sampaoli.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed trong \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, sau cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i ri\u00eang v\u1edbi Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Tapia, HLV Sampaoli v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Tapia mu\u1ed1n Sampaoli t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u00fat lui kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0110TQG, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u00ean, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 58 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV Argentina trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a World Cup v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Argentina\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/tuoi-31-cua-lionel-messi-mot-dam-me-mot-dai-kho-mot-si-389-189418.html\">Tu\u1ed5i 31 c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi: M\u1ed9t \u0111am m\u00ea, m\u1ed9t d\u1ea1i kh\u1edd, m\u1ed9t Si</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/fernando-hierro-phat-bieu-ve-dt-argentina-va-messi-421-189405.html\">T\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Argentina y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m, \u0111\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed5 t\u1ea1i Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nigeria-20-iceland-dai-bang-cuu-song-argentina-va-messi-421-189323.html\">Nigeria 2-0 Iceland: \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng\u201d c\u1ee9u s\u1ed1ng Argentina v\u00e0 Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tan-man/argentina-de-thua-croatia-khi-argentina-khong-phu-thuoc-vao-messi-392-189264.html\">Argentina \u0111\u1ec3 thua Croatia: Khi Argentina kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/argentina-that-bai-khi-sampaoli-lac-me-hon-tran-421-189252.html\">Argentina th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Khi Sampaoli l\u1ea1c m\u00ea h\u1ed3n tr\u1eadn</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"530","checkdouble":"189422"},{"date":"09:50 24/06","title":"T\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Argentina y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m, \u0111\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed5 t\u1ea1i Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/fernando-hierro-phat-bieu-ve-dt-argentina-va-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina v\u00e0 Messi sau nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1eeba qua. HLV c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Messi v\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Hierro c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng cho Messi</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110T Argentina \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. H\u1ecd h\u00f2a Iceland \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1i c\u00e3i. Qua nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Argentina, ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 Lionel Messi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nFernando Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina v\u00e0 Messi. Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho hay t\u00e0i n\u0103ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Argentina l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n m\u00ecnh Messi. \u201cT\u00f4i lu\u00f4n ngh\u0129 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u1ed1t hay x\u1ea5u r\u1ed3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u01a1i tennis\u201d, Hierro n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Onda Cero.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina v\u00e0 Messi sau nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina v\u00e0 Messi sau nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Hierro-phat-bieu-ve-DT-Argentina-va-Messi-sau-nhung-ket-qua-te-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina v\u00e0 Messi sau 2 tr\u1eadn t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t hay x\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Argentina, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hay c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3i qua. N\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 chinh ph\u1ee5c m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 c\u00e1c t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n cao qu\u00fd.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng m\u00e0 Argentina c\u00f3 v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1ea1i CLB, b\u1ea1n nh\u1eadn ra h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Alba kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u sao Messi b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Jordi Alba \u2013 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Hierro t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Messi t\u1ea1i CLB Barcelona c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn ri\u00eang. Anh l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Leo, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u00e0nh cho Messi khi c\u1ea3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Argentina ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi cung DT Argentina\" title=\"Messi cung DT Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/fernando-hierro-phat-bieu-ve-dt-argentina-va-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Alba kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u sao Messi b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Anh \u1ea5y \u0111ang b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i n\u00e0y n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Marca. \u201cArgentina ch\u01a1i hay khi c\u00f3 Messi h\u01a1n l\u00e0 khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. H\u1ecd n\u00ean t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u00ec c\u00f3 Messi trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMessi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9c nh\u1ea5t, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf 3 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u00f9ng Argentina v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Messi \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m cho \u0110TQG c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nArgentina hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D c\u1ee7a v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. H\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e1ch qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nigeria-20-iceland-dai-bang-cuu-song-argentina-va-messi-421-189323.html\">Nigeria 2-0 Iceland: \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng\u201d c\u1ee9u s\u1ed1ng Argentina v\u00e0 Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/simeone-o-cap-do-doi-tuyen-ronaldo-xuat-sac-hon-messi-421-189280.html\">Simeone: \u1ede c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ronaldo xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tan-man/argentina-de-thua-croatia-khi-argentina-khong-phu-thuoc-vao-messi-392-189264.html\">Argentina \u0111\u1ec3 thua Croatia: Khi Argentina kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Messi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"529","checkdouble":"189405"},{"date":"10:20 24/06","title":"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1, Chicharito \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/toa-sang-ruc-ro-chicharito-duoc-dong-doi-het-loi-khen-ngoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Hirving Lozano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chichario, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Mexico trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o MU.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chichario ghi b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 Mexico ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u M\u1ef9 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u1ed3n \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hirving Lozano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chichario h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hirving Lozano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chichario h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Hirving-Lozano-phat-bieu-ve-Chichario-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chicharito ghi b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nPh\u00fat 26, Carlos Vela m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat 62, Chicharito nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, anh d\u00f9ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Cho Hyun-Woo b\u1eb1ng c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Chicharito \u1edf World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o West Ham gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 2-1. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-han-quoc-vs-mexico-463-189364.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Mexico vs H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span> gi\u00fap Chicharito v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lozano khen ng\u1ee3i Chichario</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hirving Lozano ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chichario, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Mexico trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o MU.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lozano noi ve Chicharito\" title=\"Lozano n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Chicharito\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/toa-sang-ruc-ro-chicharito-duoc-dong-doi-het-loi-khen-ngoi.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lozano n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Chicharito</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng Mexico gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Chichartito, anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Chicharito \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Chicharito s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n anh \u1ea5y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn c\u00e0ng s\u00e2u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"528","checkdouble":"189406"},{"date":"09:59 24/06","title":"HLV Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n: \"\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/hlv-thuy-dien-day-la-that-bai-cay-dang-nhat-trong-su-nghiep-cam-quan-cua-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Joachim Low ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mesut Ozil kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng ngay sau trung phong Timo Werner trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t v\u00e0 C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Joachim Low ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Joachim Low ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/hlv-joachim-low-noi-gi-ve-quyet-dinh-loai-bo-mesut-ozil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Mesut Ozil ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, HLV Low v\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1 song Marco Reus l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng thay v\u00ec Ozil. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat n\u00e0o \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-o-world-cup-421-189402.html\" target=\"_blank\">Marco Reus \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng </span>trong ng\u00e0y thay th\u1ebf Ozil, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho Dortmund c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Reus, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ozil s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u01b0a l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Low c\u00f3 l\u00fd do kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Low ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Joachim Low ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ozil dinh chan thuong dau goi\" title=\"Ozil d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/cac-huyen-thoai-duc-tong-si-va-ozil-sau-cu-soc-mexico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Low tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n Ozil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c nhau t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c nhau. \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao, b\u1edfi v\u1eady t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Reus s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Ozil, b\u1edfi v\u1eady t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Reus. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t khi g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f2n v\u1edbi Ozil, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Ozil \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"527","checkdouble":"189407"},{"date":"10:19 24/06","title":"V\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, Brazil v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/lugano-khen-ngoi-neymar-va-tin-tuong-dt-brazil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Diego Lugano khen ng\u1ee3i Neymar v\u00e0 Brazil, \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn v\u00e0o h\u1ecd. C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Uruguay tin r\u1eb1ng sau khi Neymar h\u1ed3i sinh, Brazil x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Brazil thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018, \u0110T Brazil v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh. H\u1ecd h\u00f2a Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 1-1 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Costa Rica 2-0 b\u1edfi 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd c\u1ee7a Philippe Coutinho v\u00e0 Neymar.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u00f3, phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Brazil khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi xem kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. Selecao t\u1ecf ra b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Coutinho hay Neymar. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng t\u1eeb HLV Tite v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng nh\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, Brazil v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, Brazil v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Vi-dieu-nay,-Brazil-van-la-ung-vien-vo-dich-World-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Neymar v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Costa Rica 2-0 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn song Brazil v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. N\u1ebfu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Serbia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 Costa Rica, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng 5 l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi s\u1ebd s\u1edbm d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Lugano tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Brazil v\u00e0 Neymar</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 95 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Uruguay, Diego Lugano tin Brazil s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Trung v\u1ec7 t\u1eebng v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u0103m 2010 cho bi\u1ebft Selecao v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch khi h\u1ecd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u1ed3i sinh c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Neymar.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar khoc vi chien thang\" title=\"Neymar khoc vi chien thang\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/jesus-phat-bieu-ve-neymar-mit-uot-cua-dt-brazil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lugano khen ng\u1ee3i Neymar v\u00e0 Brazil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau 3 th\u00e1ng d\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u00e0n ch\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup 2018, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Costa Rica 2-0 v\u1eeba qua. &ldquo;T\u00f4i v\u1eabn ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Brazil, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t Brazil kh\u00ed th\u1ebf v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;H\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng c\u00f3 b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc. HLV Tite \u0111ang l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Brazil l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2017. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, v\u1edbi Neymar \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/brazil-thang-tran-world-cup-dau-tien-le-tru-ta-bat-dau-421-189322.html\">Brazil th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean: L\u1ec5 tr\u1eeb t\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u&hellip;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thua-thuy-sy-hlv-serbia-tuyen-chien-voi-brazil-421-189320.html\">Thua Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9, HLV Serbia tuy\u00ean chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Brazil</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-yeu-to-quyet-dinh-tran-dau-brazil-20-costa-rica-421-189317.html\">4 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 2-0 Costa Rica</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-diem-nhan-brazil-vs-costa-rica-binh-luan-brazil-vs-costa-rica-421-189305.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf c\u1ee7a Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"526","checkdouble":"189408"},{"date":"09:56 24/06","title":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Tr\u00f4ng c\u1eady h\u1ebft v\u00e0o \u201canh c\u1ea3\u201d Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/bong-da-chau-a-tai-world-cup-2018-trong-cay-het-vao-anh-ca-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i th\u00ec \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1eabn \u0111ang tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng. V\u00e0 h\u00e3y xem b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u1ebf n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 23/6, \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u00eam th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Mexico. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 phung ph\u00ed c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb x\u1ee9 s\u1edf Kim chi nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i chung cu\u1ed9c 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00f9ng Trung M\u1ef9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn hai th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean b\u1edd v\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i \u2018x\u00e1ch vali\u2019 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1edbm gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Saudi Arabia. V\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Shin Tae-yong v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ebfu th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f2n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ph\u1ea3i thua Mexico. Khi \u0111\u00f3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 nhau v\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 Tr\u00f4ng c\u1eady h\u1ebft v\u00e0o \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 Tr\u00f4ng c\u1eady h\u1ebft v\u00e0o \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Bong-da-chau-A-tai-World-Cup-2018-Trong-cay-het-vao-DT-Nhat-Ban-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn sau hai tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t to\u00e1n h\u1ecdc ch\u01b0a b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i, tuy nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c? \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y e l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 b\u1edfi th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y ngay c\u1ea3 \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n 1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Shin Tae-yong s\u1ebd theo b\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup n\u0103m nay kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi Iran v\u00e0 Australia, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ec7 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i n\u1eb1m \u1edf nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e1 phi\u1ebfu may r\u1ee7i \u0111\u01b0a Iran ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Marocco song c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Iran \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0110T Iran v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 sau pha ghi b\u00e0n c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n \u0103n may c\u1ee7a Diego Costa trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, Iran s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n m\u1ed9t B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111ang khao kh\u00e1t danh hi\u1ec7u. V\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng C, \u0110T Australia l\u00fac n\u00e0y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Peru \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ea1i D\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean 1 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dac ch\u1ea1m tay v\u00e0o t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tren cham 11 met, Jedinak khong bo lo co hoi giup Australia hoa Dan Mach, 1-1 cung la ti so chung cuoc cua tran dau.\" title=\"Tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11 m\u00e9t, Jedinak kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00fap Australia h\u00f2a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, 1-1 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/211816-12.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Australia \u00edt d\u1ea7n \u0111i\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong tay \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t \u0110T Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Do \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, \u2018nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa l\u00ednh ch\u00ec\u2019 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng C l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u00dac vs Peru. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1nh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. Khi m\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang c\u1ea7n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho v\u00f2ng trong th\u00ec m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u00f9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng v\u1eabn l\u00e0 vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Les Bleus.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Ph\u00e1p \u2018nh\u1ea3\u2019 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, Australia khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chia tay World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i k\u1ebft chung \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 khi b\u01b0\u1edbc ra s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Tr\u00f4ng c\u1eady h\u1ebft v\u00e0o \u201canh c\u1ea3\u201d Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e2n t\u00edch \u1edf tr\u00ean th\u00ec r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 g\u1ee1 g\u1ea1c l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c khi tham d\u1ef1 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 qu\u1ed1c gia s\u1edf h\u1eefu danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Asian Cup nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t (4 l\u1ea7n). Do \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u1ebfu tin r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Akira Nishino \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng H khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 Colombia 2-1 trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dieu than ky Nhat Ban\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec1u th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Nhan-dinh-Nhat-Ban-vs-Senegal-(22h00-ngay-246)-Khoc-liet-tam-ve-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u1ea3 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111ang tr\u00f4ng c\u1eady v\u00e0 'anh c\u1ea3' Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 8 n\u0103m, \u2018nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh Samurai xanh\u2019 c\u0169ng t\u1eebng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n World Cup 2010, khi h\u1ea1 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi l\u00e0 Cameroon 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 3-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 theo b\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 Lan th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng C\u0110V b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Akira Nishino s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110T Senegal s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Samurai xanh t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao khi h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u1edf th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec9nh cao phong \u0111\u1ed9. Tuy nhi\u00ean kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1edbi Senegal c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u then ch\u1ed1t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o. B\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Ba Lan \u0111ang khao kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt s\u1ebd l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u00edt.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Senegal th\u00ec chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y c\u00f2n ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u00e1ch b\u00e0i binh b\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt. \u1ede tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Colombia, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u201canh c\u1ea3\u201d ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eb7p Senegal s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1eb7p Senegal - m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i mang h\u01a1i h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t m\u00e1u l\u1eeda v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt song n\u1ebfu v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 s\u1ed1ng s\u00f3t qua v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-nhat-ban-vs-senegal-22h00-ngay-246-khoc-liet-tam-ve-di-tiep-421-189399.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/nhan-dinh-nhat-ban-vs-senegal-22h00-ngay-246-khoc-liet-tam-ve-di-tiep.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-nhat-ban-vs-senegal-22h00-ngay-246-khoc-liet-tam-ve-di-tiep-421-189399.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Senegal (22h00 ng\u00e0y 24/6): Kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</span><br>\r\nC\u1ea3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Senegal \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-colombia-12-nhat-ban-niem-vui-chua-tron-421-188990.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/du-am-colombia-12-nhat-ban-niem-vui-chua-tron.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-colombia-12-nhat-ban-niem-vui-chua-tron-421-188990.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Colombia 1-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Ni\u1ec1m vui ch\u01b0a tr\u1ecdn</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i chi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb9p tr\u1eddi t\u1ea1i Mordovia Arena, \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean qu\u1eadt ng\u00e3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Nam M\u1ef9 sau 18 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1. \u0110\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/dt-nhat-ban-lam-nen-lich-su-hay-cu-say-het-dem-nay-465-188971.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/dt-nhat-ban-lam-nen-lich-su-hay-cu-say-het-dem-nay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/dt-nhat-ban-lam-nen-lich-su-hay-cu-say-het-dem-nay-465-188971.html\">\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed: H\u00e3y c\u1ee9 say h\u1ebft \u0111\u00eam nay</span><br>\r\nNgay sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed5 ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan d\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y qu\u1eb7n \u0111au b\u1edfi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea5t t\u1eeb...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"525","checkdouble":"189409"},{"date":"11:08 24/06","title":"HLV Joachim Low n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Mesut Ozil?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/hlv-joachim-low-noi-gi-ve-quyet-dinh-loai-bo-mesut-ozil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Joachim Low ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mesut Ozil kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn thua 0-1 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng ngay sau trung phong Timo Werner trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t v\u00e0 C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua 0-1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Joachim Low ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Joachim Low ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/hlv-joachim-low-noi-gi-ve-quyet-dinh-loai-bo-mesut-ozil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Mesut Ozil ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, HLV Low v\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-2-3-1 song Marco Reus l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng thay v\u00ec Ozil. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat n\u00e0o \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-o-world-cup-421-189402.html\" target=\"_blank\">Marco Reus \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng </span>trong ng\u00e0y thay th\u1ebf Ozil, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho Dortmund c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Reus, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ozil s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u01b0a l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Low c\u00f3 l\u00fd do kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Low ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Joachim Low ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Mesut Ozil, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ozil dinh chan thuong dau goi\" title=\"Ozil d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/cac-huyen-thoai-duc-tong-si-va-ozil-sau-cu-soc-mexico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Low tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n Ozil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c nhau t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c nhau. \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao, b\u1edfi v\u1eady t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Reus s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Ozil, b\u1edfi v\u1eady t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Reus. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t khi g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f2n v\u1edbi Ozil, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Ozil \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"524","checkdouble":"189410"},{"date":"10:49 24/06","title":"\u0110\u1ee9c ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh d\u1ecb: Ng\u00e0y v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Marco Reus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/germ.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed5i danh t\u1eeb l\u00e2u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao Dortmund \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham d\u1ef1 World Cup.  S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Marco Reus trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.\r\n</h2><h2>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (B\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n VTV)\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video data-dashjs-player=\"\" src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/201806/273314/stream.mpd\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u1ec7t ng\u00e3<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Reus ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xui x\u1ebbo nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, khi anh b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia trong 4 n\u0103m v\u1eeba qua. \u0110\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u00e0 Nh\u1eefng c\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf \u0111\u1ec9nh cao th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u0103m 2014, Reus l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n trong ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u00e0 anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chia tay gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 t\u1ea1i EURO 2016 v\u00ec l\u00fd do t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi v\u1eady d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tham d\u1ef1 ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh. D\u00f9 th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t, anh l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, gi\u1eefa d\u00e0n sao Mesut Ozil hay Julian Draxler, Reus v\u1eabn l\u00e0 qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Joachim Low, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 anh kh\u00f4ng d\u1ef1 2 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marco Reus chan thuong khien anh bo lo World Cup 2014\" title=\"Marco Reus ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi\u1ebfn anh b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 World Cup 2014\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/5/31/Marco-Reus-Chiec-Rolls-Royce-kieu-sa-ma-co-don-hinh-anh-4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marco Reus li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n c\u00f9ng \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 h\u00f2a nh\u1ecbp m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Low. Ch\u1eb3ng n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2u xa, nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Marco Reus l\u00e0 ng\u00f2i n\u1ed5 ch\u00ednh trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee3t l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Die Mannschaft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, s\u1ed1 11 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, <strong>m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u00fd ki\u1ebfn c\u00f2n lo ng\u1ea1i anh&hellip; g\u00e3y ch\u00e2n v\u00ec v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh. </strong>Nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt may, chi\u1ebfc \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0nh l\u1eb7n v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng, v\u00e0 gi\u00fap Reus c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed World Cup. \u0110\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng anh v\u1eabn t\u1ea1o ra n\u00e9t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00e0 su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ed1n s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, nh\u01b0ng Reus c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o sau l\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn so v\u1edbi Mesut Ozil ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 10, hay Draxler \u01b0a th\u00edch b\u00e1m bi\u00ean tr\u00e1i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1. S\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 \u00fd th\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt gi\u00fap Reus lu\u00f4n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y Joachim Low.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ee9c ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh d\u1ecb Ng\u00e0y v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Marco Reus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110\u1ee9c ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kinh d\u1ecb Ng\u00e0y v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Marco Reus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/100449-reu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Reus ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a gi\u00fap \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Marco Reus</h2>\r\n<p>Ngay trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup, Reus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 trong vai tr\u00f2 s\u1ed1 10, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y ra c\u00e1nh thay Draxler r\u1eddi s\u00e2n, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Dortmund m\u1edbi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t. 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 1 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Kroos, ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u1ebfu so s\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, Reus ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o. Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0o, ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00fang 2 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t \u00edt, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi 2 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p v\u00e0o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. M\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ham b\u00f3ng hay \u01b0a bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u tham d\u1ef1 &ndash; tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau m\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 Ronaldo, Neymar.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, \u1edf Marco Reus lu\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd t\u1eeb b\u1ecf, sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng nghi\u1ec7t ng\u00e3 anh tr\u1ea3i qua trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i s\u1ed1ng chung v\u1edbi c\u00e1i d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nguy\u00ean v\u1eb9n, anh c\u00f2n g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 e ng\u1ea1i? Nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u1edbi Reus, khi anh \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Reus va Kroos giup Duc loi nguoc dong thanh cong\" title=\"Reus v\u00e0 Kroos gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/Hummels-lo-lang-cho-DT-Duc-sau-khi-thang-thot-tim-Thuy-Dien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Reus v\u00e0 Kroos gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\nV\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Reus l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean hi\u1ebfm hoi v\u1eabn gi\u1eef v\u1eefng tinh th\u1ea7n c\u00f9ng Toni Kroos. H\u1ecd v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o, d\u00f9 Jerome Boateng v\u1eeba nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Dortmund, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 thi \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n, ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngh\u1ec9 6 th\u00e1ng, r\u1ed3i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c c\u00f3&hellip; hattrick. \u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Marco Reus kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd b\u1ecb gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, d\u00f9 th\u1eddi gian n\u1eb1m vi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a anh c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u. L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh World Cup, 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o &ndash; Marco Reus ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ec1 coi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0o m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>&ldquo;Cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3i qua, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh&rdquo;</strong> &ndash; \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e2u n\u00f3i Marco Reus x\u0103m \u1edf b\u1eafp tay tr\u00e1i, gi\u1ed1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi t\u1ef1 nh\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u d\u1ef1 World Cup, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 29, nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u c\u1ee7a Marco Reus gi\u1edd m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Duc 2-1 Thuy Dien\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/Thong-so-Duc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-o-world-cup-421-189402.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-o-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/marco-reus-noi-gi-sau-ban-thang-dau-tien-o-world-cup-421-189402.html\">Trai \u0111\u1eb9p Marco Reus n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf World Cup</span><br>\r\nMarco Reus n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Dortmund kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0110\u1ee9c x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-dau-tim-cua-dt-duc-421-189380.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/Hummels-lo-lang-cho-DT-Duc-sau-khi-thang-thot-tim-Thuy-Dien-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-chien-thang-dau-tim-cua-dt-duc-421-189380.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111au tim c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1edbm, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Joachim Low v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-thuy-dien-461-189377.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/20180623T190726Z_938071254_RC1A5344D010_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPGERSWE.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-duc-vs-thuy-dien-461-189377.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110\u1ee9c 2-1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (B\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nSau hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1eeda t\u1eed (Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc), Mannschaft \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh tinh th\u1ea7n gh\u00ea g\u1edbm \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"523","checkdouble":"189411"},{"date":"11:12 24/06","title":"MU quy\u1ec7t chi 166 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Martial","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/mu-quyet-chi-166-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-martial.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Kylian Mbappe c\u1ee7a PSG trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Anthony Martial r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anthony Martial tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p t\u1edbi Nga d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Kylian Mbappe thay Anthony Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Kylian Mbappe thay Anthony Martial h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/MU-muon-mua-Kylian-Mbappe-thay-Anthony-Martial-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martial mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi MU \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Martial l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p, khi Mourinho l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Sanchez \u00f4ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean Rashford h\u01a1n l\u00e0 c\u1ef1u sao Monaco. Ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean anh \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, Philippe Lamboley kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-tien-dao-martial-tuyen-bo-chia-tay-mu-172-188440.html\" target=\"_blank\">Martial c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd r\u1eddi M.U</span> \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cSau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i suy ngh\u0129, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u00ean r\u1eddi M.U. Martial n\u0103m nay 23 tu\u1ed5i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU mua Mbappe thay Martial</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao thay th\u1ebf. MU mu\u1ed1n mua Kylian Mbappe c\u1ee7a PSG trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Anthony Martial r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mua Mbappe thay Martial\" title=\"MU mua Mbappe thay Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/mu-quyet-chi-166-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-martial.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mua Mbappe thay Martial</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o PSG, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng sao tr\u1ebb s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Hi\u1ec7n PSG \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y PSG \u0111\u00e3 chi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi \u0111\u1eadm \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng vi ph\u1ea1m lu\u1eadt C\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh do UEFA quy \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi PSG c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i sao quan tr\u1ecdng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Neymar nh\u01b0ng Mbappe ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 166 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Sunday Mirror, MU th\u1eadm ch\u00ed d\u00f9ng Martial c\u1ed9ng 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c PSG b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 PSG s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu Martial trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"522","checkdouble":"189412"},{"date":"11:36 24/06","title":"Barca, Real v\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/6/barca-real-va-psg-dai-chien-vi-sao-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real, Barca v\u00e0 PSG l\u00e0 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kante \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 N'Golo Kante duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real, Barca v\u00e0 PSG mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real, Barca v\u00e0 PSG mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/19/Real,-Barca-va-PSG-muon-dua-tien-ve-Kante-roi-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kante \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 s\u1edf h\u1eefu n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p t\u1ed1t, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n trong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi. Kante c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra th\u00f4ng minh trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Kante c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap Les Bleus ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn h\u1ecfi mua Kante</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real, Barca v\u00e0 PSG l\u00e0 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real, Barca v\u00e0 PSG mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Real, Barca v\u00e0 PSG mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/6/barca-real-va-psg-dai-chien-vi-sao-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn h\u1ecfi mua NGolo Kante</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLe Parisien kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1t ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/psg-chi-so-tien-sieu-khung-mua-sao-chelsea-172-188620.html\" target=\"_blank\">PSG m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Kante</span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Antero Henrique c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kante, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u00e2ng l\u00ean 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKante c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2021, The Blues kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. Song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfi mua Kante, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"521","checkdouble":"189414"},{"date":"11:32 24/06","title":"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y 24/6:  Messi s\u1ebd \"d\u1eabn d\u1eaft\" tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u1edf tr\u1eadn \"chung k\u1ebft\" v\u1edbi Nigeria","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/23/ngay-hom-nay-246.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi n\u00f3ng hot nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay (24/6). Nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1eebng chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMessi s\u1ebd \"d\u1eabn d\u1eaft\" tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u1edf tr\u1eadn \"chung k\u1ebft\" v\u1edbi Nigeria\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 246 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin n\u00f3ng World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay, tin t\u1ee9c World Cup ng\u00e0y 246 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/fernando-hierro-phat-bieu-ve-dt-argentina-va-messi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Daily Mail, gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c AFA (L\u0110B\u0110 Argentina), \u00f4ng Jorge Burruchaga cho bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i HLV Jorge Sampaoli, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ef1 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i: \"Sampaoli \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u01b0\u1edbc quy\u1ec1n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb n\u1ebfu \u00f4ng ta mu\u1ed1n\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMessi v\u00e0 Mascherano, 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m d\u00e0y d\u1ea1n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0a Argentina l\u00e1ch qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i. Argentina c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi Iceland kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay.</div>\r\n<h2>Brazil nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Serbia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">ESPN \u0111\u01b0a tin Costa \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00f9i trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc Costa Rica. Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 23/6, b\u00e1c s\u0129 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ki\u1ec3m tra t\u1ed5ng qu\u00e1t cho cho Costa v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRodrigo Lasmar, b\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Brazil, n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 mang \u00e1o 7: \u201cCu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u00f9i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Costa tr\u1ea3i qua c\u01a1n \u0111au kh\u00e1 d\u1eef d\u1ed9i. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cho th\u1ea5y ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Costa kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi\u201d.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/1_5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n lao v\u00e0o xung \u0111\u1ed9t sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i th\u1ed5i c\u00f2i k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n c\u00e3i v\u00e3 gay g\u1eaft ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch. HLV Janne Andersson c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn khi cho r\u1eb1ng khi Kroos ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1y v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c \u0103n m\u1eebng tr\u00eau ng\u01b0\u01a1i ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Andersson c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u1eadm h\u1ef1c n\u00f3i: \"Sau pha \u0103n m\u1eebng \u1ea5y, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong s\u1ed1 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng trong su\u1ed1t 95 ph\u00fat, r\u1ed3i khi ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i c\u1ea5t l\u00ean, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1eaft tay r\u1ed3i b\u1ecf \u0111i. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn\".</div>\r\n<h2>Southgate ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn l\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Trong bu\u1ed5i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Southgate t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb l\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt nh\u01b0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u01b0a tin. \"T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y. Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn Panama. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n nh\u1ecf trong nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\".\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-southgate-noi-ve-kha-nang-ra-san-cua-tru-cot-truoc-tran-gap-panama-421-189344.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/23/hlv-southgate-noi-ve-kha-nang-ra-san-cua-tru-cot-truoc-tran-gap-panama.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-southgate-noi-ve-kha-nang-ra-san-cua-tru-cot-truoc-tran-gap-panama-421-189344.html\">HLV Southgate n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Panama</span><br>\r\n<span>Gareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Dele Alli, HLV tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Tunisia xin l\u1ed7i C\u0110V</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau khi thua 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u Phi g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, HLV Nabil Maaloul xin l\u1ed7i C\u0110V v\u00e0 k\u00eau g\u1ecdi Tunisia c\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0 B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i xin g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u1eeba qua. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Tunisia c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i t\u1ed5 l\u1ea1i c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c s\u00e1nh vai c\u00f9ng Anh hay B\u1ec9\".</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \"ng\u1ea1i\" nh\u1ea5t Mane</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a \"Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh Samurai xanh\", HLV Akira Nishino t\u1ecf ra quan ng\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t Sadio Mane, ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Senegal. \"Sadio Mane s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00f9ng n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1ch Mane g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i lo ng\u1ea1i h\u01a1n c\u1ea3\".\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-nhat-ban-vs-senegal-22h00-ngay-246-khoc-liet-tam-ve-di-tiep-421-189399.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n vs Senegal (22h00 ng\u00e0y 24/6): Kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"520","checkdouble":"189415"}]}